|YCBThe wayfarians are a race of elves that have been oppressed by forces of evil
for as long as their culture has been around. A powerful Paladin heroine
'Enelya Ar-Feiniel' who is now revered as their patron of adventurers sought
out Mitra's blessing to empower and protect her proud folk. This blessing
resulted in a holy and virtuous aura surrounding each member of the Wayfarian
race. This aura formed a defense against the evil acts of their foes and 
enabled them to strike out with a holy fury. Finally the Wayfarians were able 
to beat off their oppressors and build a new city. Their combined auras
helped form a powerful holy dome to protect this city against those who 
would seek to destroy it.

